As expected on the red carpet, the celebrities never disappoint because they always show up dressed to the nines. When the said event now turns out to be a fashion award, then you can expect to see nothing but the best of the best and that is exactly what we saw at the 2019 CFDA Fashion Awards that held on June 3 in New York. From Jennifer Lopez who was the recipient of this year’s Fashion Icon Award to supermodels like Kendall Jenner, Bella and Gigi Hadid, Ashley Graham, Emily Ratajkowski and more all looking elegant in their evening gowns. There were so many gorgeous outfits at the CFDA Awards, and we have rounded up all of the best looks from the night. See photos below: